OL,3,CMuseum workers start eight-week strike
OL,4,Cover pay
OL,6,FMuseum and art gallery staff are
OL,7,Fstarting an eight-week strike in a
OL,8,Fdispute over pay.
OL,10,FMore than 200 members of the Public
OL,11,Fand Commercial Services union (PCS) at
OL,12,FNational Museums Liverpool (NML) will
OL,13,Ftake industrial action which begins on
OL,14,FSaturday.
OL,16,FThe union says the strike is likely to
OL,17,Faffect four of the city's museums; the
OL,18,FMuseum of Liverpool, the World Museum,
OL,19,Fthe International Slavery Museum and
OL,20,Fthe Maritime Museum.
