OL,6,FGallery staff at the Walker Art
OL,7,FGallery, Sudley House and the Lady
OL,8,FLever Art Gallery are also part of the
OL,9,Findustrial action.
OL,11,FThe NML is the only one of more than
OL,12,F200 employers not to have honoured a
OL,13,F#1,500 payment which helped resolve a
OL,14,Fnational dispute last year.
OL,16,FPCS general secretary Fran Heathcote
OL,17,Fsaid: "PCS has tried our hardest to
OL,18,Fresolve this dispute, but we have been
OL,19,Fmet with a straight 'No' from the
OL,20,Femployer.
