OL,6,F"Our fight is not with those people
OL,7,Fwho visit the museums ` it's with
OL,8,Fthose who undervalue our members'
OL,9,Fpassion, skill and knowledge at work.
OL,11,F"It's time for NML to pay up and
OL,12,Frecognise the contribution our members
OL,13,Fmake to the economic and cultural
OL,14,Fwellbeing of Liverpool."
